                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If the victim succeeds at a saving throw against this curse while in sunlight, the curse ends. While you have this curse, you bypass the resistance of the wraith that cursed you;</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:will|dc:24]</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> the victim is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] in any light (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> the victim gains lifesense 30 feet but is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] in any light (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> as stage 2, but the creature also has @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Item.Void Healing] (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> the victim becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Unconscious] and can't awaken (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> the creature dies and becomes a wraith, its body crumbling to ash</p>"
